data.description: Welcome to your Pinterest-perfect home, a dreamy haven where style and comfort intertwine flawlessly. From the moment you step through the charming front door, you'll be captivated by the inviting atmosphere and curated aesthetics that celebrate both modern elegance and cozy nostalgia. Perfect layout with plenty of storage, great natural light throughout, large detached 30x20 building. Nicely positioned on a dead-end street. Enjoy the sunsets from the back porch. There is even the perfect spot for your 4 legged friends off the kitchen!
